        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>This Privacy Policy explains how Backyard Math may collect, use, and protect information when you visit this website.</p>

        <h2>Information we collect</h2>
        <p>Backyard Math does not require user accounts, logins, or contact forms. We do not intentionally collect personal information that you submit directly to us through the website.</p>
        <p>Like most websites, this site may collect non-personal usage information automatically, such as browser type, device type, pages visited, referring pages, approximate location, and general website activity.</p>

        <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
        <p>This website may use cookies or similar technologies to understand how visitors use the site, improve performance, measure traffic, and analyze popular pages.</p>
        <p>We use Google Analytics to help understand website usage. This tool may collect information according to its own privacy policy.</p>

        <h2>Advertising</h2>
        <p>This website may display third-party advertisements in the future, including ads served by networks such as Google AdSense or similar advertising partners.</p>
        <p>Advertising partners may use cookies, web beacons, or similar technologies to serve ads, measure ad performance, prevent fraud, and personalize advertising where permitted by law.</p>

        <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
        <p>This website may include affiliate links in the future. If you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, the site may earn a commission at no additional cost to you.</p>

        <h2>Third-party websites</h2>
        <p>This website may link to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices, content, policies, or actions of third-party websites.</p>

        <h2>Data security</h2>
        <p>We use reasonable measures to keep the website secure, but no website or internet transmission can be guaranteed to be completely secure.</p>

        <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
        <p>This website is intended for general audiences and is not directed toward children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

        <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

